== Board members ==
Board members are elected and unlike the Board of Governors, their function is to attend business meetings and handle the everyday administration of the academy.<ref name="urlAcademy of Television Arts & Sciences">{{cite web |url=http://www.emmys.tv/executive-committee |title=Academy of Television Arts & Sciences |author=[[Academy of Television Arts & Sciences|ATAS]] |authorlink= |coauthors= |date= |format= |work= |publisher= |pages= |language= |archiveurl= |archivedate= |quote= |accessdate=2010-07-08}}Board of Directors</ref>
